body_html:
This cl broke a lot of tests internally. I will rerun tests to see if the issues reproduce on these tests.

I accidentally missed adding posix_cmake_vars after several rebasing and resolving merge conflict. f419d81 should fix the XLA test for POSIX platforms.

body:
> This cl broke a lot of tests internally. I will rerun tests to see if the issues reproduce on these tests.

I accidentally missed adding `posix_cmake_vars` after several rebasing and resolving merge conflict. https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/pull/18293/commits/f419d81a85425d51661adcbbe198ffd2b343568a should fix the XLA test for POSIX platforms.
